Title: Teliko
Plot: After several African-American men are killed and the color is drained from their skin, Mulder learns about the Teliko, an African folktale about a creature who must suck the pigmentation from a persons body in order to survive.
GuestStars: Maxine Guess, Michael O'Shea, Don Stewart, Geoffrey Aye-Bonte, Dexter Bell, Carl Lumbly, Willie Amakye, Zakes Mokae, Bob Morrisey
